# What's Preinstalled

BlossomOS ships with a curated set of apps so it's usable right after installation, without needing to hunt down the basics yourself. Everything below is installed automatically as a Flatpak the first time you boot or update, on top of the standard KDE Plasma desktop (Dolphin, Konsole, System Settings, and so on).

Anything here can be removed if you don't need it, and reinstalled again from Arc Store at any time.

