## BlossomUI

BlossomOS also ships its own Plasma style, window decoration, and icon theme, collectively called **BlossomUI**, giving the desktop its default look. It isn't an app you launch, it's what makes the whole system look like BlossomOS out of the box.

## Missing Something?

Not seeing an app you'd expect? Check **[Arc Store](./arc-store)** first, most software is just a search away. If you think something should ship preinstalled by default, open an issue on **[Blossom Git](https://dev.blossomos.org/blossom)**.
